{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Synopsis</h2>Location is the ancient capital city Nanjing, China. And time is when spring turns into summer.<br><br>While visiting his sick father, college student Wei Qiuwu accidentally encountered a concertina playing little girl in the hospital.<br>An inharmonious pair, seemingly. But soon, Wei Qiuwu became a good friend of Li Jiayun, the little player. And both of them act as an indispensable tune in each other's life.<br>With the accompaniment of sedate Nurse Yang Qin and cheerful high school student He Jia, the story surrounding Li Jiayun is about to begin...<br><br>After they get familiar with each other, He Jia guides Wei Qiuwu and Li Jiayun to visit a lot of interesting places, acquaint with a variety of people and encounter with a diversity of things.<br>They become an inseparable trio as well as good friends, everything looks blissful. Until one day, Yang Qin unveiled to Wei Qiuwu the cruel truth under a fairy-tale cover...<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The official sequel of Shan Gui.<br></li><li>A storyline of 8 to 12 hours, with multiple routes and endings.<br></li><li>There is no absolute &quot;right choice&quot;, different endings contain different meaning.<br></li><li>An unordinary story, themed with love and caring in ordinary daily life.<br></li><li>A modern story happened in an ancient country.<br></li><li>Full-voiced main characters.<br></li><li>Delicate and realistic background pictures, field recorded ambient sound to make you feel you were in the scene.<br></li><li>Over 20 wonderful background music tracks, which include varieties of music genres.<br></li><li>2560\u00d71440 resolution for game and 4096\u00d72304 for CGs.</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"A Notebook","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/516600/8ca561e5126f843cff917cf2b91a707f6d1ef2c7.jpg"},{"name":"Unexpected Encounter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.stea